{"tid":2047044,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登訪示威區與黑人對話，拜登：我11月當選總統後，將帶領對話，爭取黑人權益","createTime":"2020-06-02T00:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T05:17:50.000Z","uid":202698,"like":1,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"6b3be8137dee26b68bd861857e1ab7ac8122800a","tid":2047044,"uid":202698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T00:05:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZDewhpc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZDewhpc.jpg&h=d6a92282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%AA%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E5%8D%80%E8%88%87%E9%BB%91%E4%BA%BA%E7%88%B6%E5%AD%90%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1-214500220.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%258B%259C%25E7%2599%25BB%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%2588%2587%25E9%25BB%2591%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2588%25B6%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25A9%25B1-214500220.html&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbQKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=129f3a2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%AA%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E5%8D%80%E8%88%87%E9%BB%91%E4%BA%BA%E7%88%B6%E5%AD%90%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1-214500220.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報綜合報道】美國民主黨總統參選人、前副總統拜登前日低調往特拉華州的示威地點視察，是他三月返回特拉華州避疫後，第二次公開露面。<br />\n<br />\n有分析指，爭取連任的總統特朗普揚言動武平亂，旨在鞏固保守選民的支持，以爭取今年大選連任。<span style=\"color: red;\">拜登若要挑戰總統寶座，就要利用今次反警暴示威，爭取更多年輕人支持。</span><br />\n<br />\n戴着口罩的拜登抵達威爾明頓，與黑人居民對話，並視察一處封鎖防止示威者衝擊的建築物。拜登其後在社交網Twitter上載照片，可見他單膝下跪，與一對黑人父子交談。他寫道，美國處於痛苦之中，但絕不能被這痛苦摧毀；<span style=\"color: red;\">揚言當選總統後會帶領對話及傾聽，如同他到威爾明頓視察一樣。</span><br />\n<br />\n迎合右翼 特朗普言論被批撥火<br />\n<br />\n特朗普近日多次在Twitter發文譴責暴力示威，形容示威者是暴徒，甚至將矛頭指向激進左翼組織。雖然外界批評特朗普令局勢惡化、加劇社會撕裂，但有指他利用動亂時刻爭取右翼選民的支持。<br />\n<br />\n共和黨金主、特朗普支持者埃伯哈特（Dan Eberhart）表示，特朗普專注迎合他的核心支持者，而不是整個國家；並形容特朗普比以往的總統「更分裂」。有官員建議，特朗普可以趁機走鐵腕路線及打出經濟牌，向財產受破壞的商家傳達保護他們的利益的訊息。"},{"pid":"9f11545a1dad8fb3e8f2729e991044256b2ec179","tid":2047044,"uid":270220,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T00:49:34.000Z","msg":"空頭支票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e665ce219ab2dd60ab45ee62a1b4044e96492a","tid":2047044,"uid":21063,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T00:50:03.000Z","msg":"要做嘢2008-2016做咗啦"},{"pid":"e02ea4333d76a27069a6a0517699bb06d36773e0","tid":2047044,"uid":47492,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"9f11545a1dad8fb3e8f2729e991044256b2ec179","tid":2047044,"uid":270220,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T00:49:34.000Z","msg":"空頭支票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T00:53:04.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜就係咁上位"},{"pid":"f9e7246280e4203725005c38cee3f5a27ac7f398","tid":2047044,"uid":11447,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T00:53:54.000Z","msg":"暴動指揮官"},{"pid":"8de96d74f52cabbec75d12c3335b86df6d48aeee","tid":2047044,"uid":179718,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e02ea4333d76a27069a6a0517699bb06d36773e0","tid":2047044,"uid":47492,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"9f11545a1dad8fb3e8f2729e991044256b2ec179","tid":2047044,"uid":270220,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T00:49:34.000Z","msg":"空頭支票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T00:53:04.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜就係咁上位"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T00:54:16.000Z","msg":"美國發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cfdc0840a28a17dbf5653d8d90efa9e0660c6bf","tid":2047044,"uid":47492,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8de96d74f52cabbec75d12c3335b86df6d48aeee","tid":2047044,"uid":179718,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e02ea4333d76a27069a6a0